videos.description: Udoka Azubuike catches the lob pass and throws down a powerful dunk with one hand over the defender.
videos.headline: Azubuike throws down dunk on top of defender

videos.description: Oscar da Silva uses the pump fake to lose three defenders and get the easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Stanford's da Silva jukes 3 defenders for easy score

videos.description: Stanford's Trevor Stanback rises up to grab the lob pass and throws down a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Stanback grabs lob for dunk

videos.description: Kansas takes the lead after Lagerald Vick nails a shot from deep.
videos.headline: Vick nails deep shot for the lead

videos.description: Lagerald Vick pulls up for a quick 3-pointer and sinks it to tie the game and send it to overtime.
videos.headline: Vick drains 3-pointer to send game to OT

videos.description: Lagerald Vick leaves his defender in the dust with a crossover move and elevates to throw down a dunk over a Stanford defender.
videos.headline: Vick throws down dunk on defender

videos.description: Lagerald Vick sinks a three after losing his balance on a crossover move.
videos.headline: Vick sinks pull-up 3-pointer
